quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  19,96,"Pellet, ɓeen gooɗinɓe ngolli ko moƴƴi ko aray ka jurmotooɗo waɗanaɓe Giggol."
  19,97,"Anndu ko min n newiniri nde ka ɗenngal maaɗa; ko fii yo a weltinir nde hulooɓe [Alla] ɓen njertiniraa nde yimɓe saɗtuɓe weeñre."
  19,98,"Heewii ko min kalki ado maɓɓe e gire taw si hiɗa so'a e maɓɓe immorde e goɗɗo, maa haɗa nana ɓe hito?"
  20,1,"Taa Haa."
  20,2,"Min Telliniraani Alqur'aanaare nde e maaɗa fii yo a tampu."
  20,3,"Si wonaa waaju wonan'de on kuloowo [Alla]."
  20,4,"Ko Jippinaande immorde e oon takɗo leydi ndi e kammuuji toowuɗi ɗin."
  20,5,"Jurmotooɗ o O fotii e dow Arsi he."
  20,6,"No woodani mo o ko woni ko e kammuuji ɗin e ko woni kon e leydi ndi e ko wini kon hakkunde majji kannji ɗiɗi e ko woni ko e les leydi."
  20,7,"Si a fenñinii konngol ngol, pellet, Kaŋko homo Anndi ko feeñi e ko o suuɗi."
  20,8,"Alla deweteeɗo alaa si wonaa Kaŋko, no woodani mo Inɗe moƴƴe ɗe."
  20,9,"taw si arii e maaɗa yewtere fii Muusaa."
  20,10,"Tuma nde o yi'inoo yiite, o wi'ani ɓeynguure makko nden: "Ñiiɓee, min de mi haynike jayngol mbele-jo'o mi addanat on immorde e maggol docotal ma mi tawa ka [moggo] yiite tinndinoowo."
  20,11,"Tuma nde o aunoo e maggol o noddaa; "eyma Muusaa"."
  20,12,"[Alla Daalano mo] Min dey ko miin Woni Joomi maaɗa poortu paɗe maa ɗen; pellet an, haɗa ka aynde(caatngol) Tuwaa Laɓɓinaande(seninangol)."